{"product_id":"veni-vidi-vici-hoodie","title":"VENI VIDI VICI HOODIE","description":"\u003cp\u003e MALE MODEL HEIGHT 5'10 AND WAIST SIZE 32 WEARING M HOODIE.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e 420 GSM\u003cbr\u003e PREMIUM 100% COTTON FLEECE\u003cbr\u003e COMBED \u0026amp; BIO-WASHED FINISH\u003cbr\u003e HIGH-DENSITY PRINT ON FRONT, BACK \u0026amp; SLEEVES\u003cbr\u003e TWO-WAY YKK ZIPPER WITH DOUBLE-LAYERED HOOD\u003cbr\u003e KANGAROO POCKETS\u003cbr\u003e BAGGY FIT\u003cbr\u003e UNISEX ARTICLE [REFER TO SIZE CHART FOR ACCURATE MEASUREMENTS]. \u003c\/p\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eUltra-heavy 420 GSM fabric delivers superior durability, structure, and comfort.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eClean DRIP STUDIOS branding on the front for a refined statement.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eIntricate streetwear-inspired artwork printed along the sleeves for added edge.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eBold “VENI VIDI VICI” high-density print on the back ensures standout impact.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eCombed and bio-washed finish provides a soft hand feel and long-lasting color.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eTwo-way YKK zipper offers versatility, ease of wear, and premium functionality.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eDouble-layered hood enhances structure, warmth, and elevated styling.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eDesigned for confident, everyday wear with a strong visual identity.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e \u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eMachine wash the hoodie inside out with like colors.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eUse cold water to preserve fabric quality and print integrity.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eTumble dry on low heat or air dry to maintain shape and prevent shrinkage.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eStore in a cool, dry place to protect the fabric and finish.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e \u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eHoodie constructed with 420 GSM fabric for a substantial, premium feel.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eBaggy fit designed for relaxed comfort and versatile styling.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eUnisex article suitable for a wide range of body types.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eFront pouch pocket for everyday convenience and warmth.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eSoft, breathable jersey backing ensures comfort and airflow.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eLong sleeves with ribbed cuffs and hem for a secure, structured fit.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"XS","offer_id":46853859246234,"sku":"HOODIES(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2678.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"S","offer_id":46853859082394,"sku":"HOODIES(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2678.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":46853859115162,"sku":"HOODIES(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2678.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":46853859147930,"sku":"HOODIES(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2678.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46853859180698,"sku":"HOODIES(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2678.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46853859213466,"sku":"HOODIES(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2678.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/D5F11384-8EF7-4862-83B4-C33F532BEF51.png?v=1769967207","url":"https:\/\/dripdrip.in\/products\/veni-vidi-vici-hoodie","provider":"DRIP STUDIOS","version":"1.0","type":"link"}